@BpmApiHost_HostAddress = http://localhost:5162

### 启动流程
POST {{BpmApiHost_HostAddress}}/api/bpm/process/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processDefinitionKey": "expense-approval",
  "initiator": "zhangsan",
  "variables": {
    "amount": 1200
  }
}

### 查询待办
GET {{BpmApiHost_HostAddress}}/api/bpm/tasks/pending?assignee=zhangsan
Accept: application/json
